com.laegler.fastbpmn.mapping

Class FastBpmnToBpmn

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.laegler.fastbpmn.mapping.FastBpmnToBpmn

  • public class FastBpmnToBpmn
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements mapping from FastBPMN which is an EMF object tree to BPMN 2.0 which is also an EMF object tree. There is also a serializiation feature for exporting the BPMN2 tree to a valid XML-based BPMN 2.0 file with the file extension *.bpmn.
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Thomas Laegler
